  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Wisdom</b> is the title used by full-fledged members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, a learned society that knows how to make <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a>. They are known colloquially as <i>pyromancers</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Wisdoms\">Known Wisdoms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wisdom&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Wisdoms\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rossart\" title=\"Rossart\">Rossart</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_master\" title=\"Grand master\">grand master</a> of the Alchemists' Guild</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garigus\" title=\"Garigus\">Garigus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Belis\" title=\"Belis\">Belis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pollitor\" title=\"Pollitor\">Pollitor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hallyne\" title=\"Hallyne\">Hallyne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Munciter\" title=\"Munciter\">Munciter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Malliard\" title=\"Malliard\">Malliard</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wisdom&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Master\" c